HEADWORD: Enslavement
<hw>En*slave"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
reducing to slavery; state of being enslaved; bondage;
servitude.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A fresh <qex>enslavement</qex> to their enemies.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

